text: Saboh golongan nibak awaknyan Jikheun bak ureueng nyang di Madinah Hai awak Yasrib di sinoe hana Ã­ Teumpat keu gata hana geukeubah Tajakwoe keudeh bek le disinan Saboh golongan jikheun le bagah Jilakee izin jijak bak Nabi Kamoe keumbali ya Rasulullah Hana soe tinggai rumoh kamoe soh Atra hana soh meuka jipeugah Napsu jimeung plueng bek roh lam kawan
